      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SAN SABA (1) had been about the mark in recent runs before the latest appearance when she finished 13 metres away in third over 2200m at this track. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw. Big chance in this comparable race. MULLUM DOC (7) scored at Redcliffe two runs ago before having his colours lowered when ninth at his latest appearance over 1780m at Redcliffe, beaten 22 metres. Drawn to enjoy a cosy run but might need things to go his way at some stage. Ideally placed and is sure to prove tough to beat. MILLIEWOOD (6) is better than her last-start eighth over 1660m at Albion Park. Worth considering. MAYWYN TROUBADOUR (5) is in the mix following a fourth at his first run back over 1780m at Redcliffe.",
